# Project Structure

This is a React portfolio website built with Vite and styled with Tailwind CSS.

## Main Files
- [main.jsx](mdc:src/main.jsx) - Entry point for the React application
- [App.jsx](mdc:src/App.jsx) - Main application component that handles routing
- [index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global CSS styles and Tailwind imports

## Component Structure
The UI is built with modular components located in [src/components/](mdc:src/components/):
- [Hero.jsx](mdc:src/components/Hero.jsx) - Hero section with CV download
- [Navbar.jsx](mdc:src/components/Navbar.jsx) - Navigation component
- [About.jsx](mdc:src/components/About.jsx) - About section
- [Experience.jsx](mdc:src/components/Experience.jsx) - Work experience section
- [Work.jsx](mdc:src/components/Work.jsx) - Projects showcase
- [Contact.jsx](mdc:src/components/Contact.jsx) - Contact form

## Assets
- Public assets like downloadable files are stored in [public/](mdc:public/)
